Replaces the HUD with a beautiful, simple: Green, Dark & White HUD; [Server-Side]

Elements Replaced:

[code]
- All Ammo Types
- HP
- Armor
- Syringe
- Welder
- Text Colors
- Border/Box Colors
- Wave Indicator
- Time Indicator
- Trader Arrow
- Magazine Clip
- Grenades
- PipeBombs
- Perk Stars/Levels
- Inventory Overlay
[/code]

Elements Fixed:

[code]
- All Text alignments
- All Icons aligned on same Y-Axis
- Fix for Weight numbers being so wonky from TWI code (Made them as Numeric Widgets)
[/code]

Elements that haven't been changed yet:

[code]
- Perk Icons[/strike]
[/code]

[H1][b][u]Whitelist Status[/u][/b][/H1]

- NO | Requires client-side modifications

[H1][b][u]Number Of Files[/u][/b][/H1]

- 4

[H1][b][u]File Names[/u][/b][/H1]

- \System\ColorfulHUD.u
- \System\ColorfulHUD.ucl

- \Textures\ColorfulHUD.utx

- \StaticMeshes\GreenShopArrow.usx

[H1][b][u]Usage[/u][/b][/H1]

1- Subscribe or download manually (recommended)
2- Launch the game and wait to see 'Completed'
3- Restart the game and you can see the mutators in your list

[H1][b][u]Class Names[/u][/b][/H1]

- ColorfulHUD.ColorfulHUD

